---
title: Cinnamon Lamb Ragu with Rigatoni and Feta
description: Here at HelloFresh we're all about bringing variety to dinnertime and helping you to climb out of culinary ruts. It's so easy to get stuck in habits. Like automatically reaching for the beef mince when making a pasta sauce. Why not ring the changes and try lamb instead? In tonight's dinner it makes a richly flavoured ragu served with rigatoni, crumbled feta and parsley. Enjoy!
